	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗚哇！<delay20 />你那張臉！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難不成<delay8 />是被黃蜂螫到了？<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牠們很兇暴，<delay20 />
你可要多加小心才行<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但現在說這些，<delay8 />好像已經太遲了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇啊，<delay20 />你那張臉是怎麼回事！？<delay40 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然跟人打架打成這樣，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也真是調皮呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦<tag a="110" b="0" />？<delay20 />不是打架，是黃蜂？<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什麼呀，原來是被黃蜂螫到喔！<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />反正都一樣，<delay8 />只要塗個<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />，很快就能痊癒囉！</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你那張臉<delay8 />是怎麼啦！？<delay40 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看你的臉變得這麼狂野，<delay20 />
簡直讓我嚇一大跳！<pageBreak /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難不成<delay8 />是被黃蜂螫到了？<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然放著不管，<delay8 />應該也會痊癒，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過要是想快點治好，就塗個<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗚哇！<delay8 />你那張臉<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />該不會是被黃蜂螫到吧？<delay40 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是的，<delay20 />你也太遲鈍了吧！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我把買來應急用的<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />送你，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你拿去治療吧！<delay40 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以後不可以<delay8 />再這樣亂來了喔！</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過說歸說，其實我小時候<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也經常去騷擾蜂巢，<delay8 />
結果被黃蜂螫得滿臉都是呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />老媽經常叮嚀我<delay20 />
「至少身上要隨時帶著<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />」！<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能派上用場，真是太好啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
