	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />對了！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不巧我的<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />剛好用完了，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我知道作法，就教你怎麼做吧。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要收集到那份方程式裡寫的材料，
